Hey! If you don’t give up! You can’t fail! Keep Going! I had to start my life over 3 years ago.
Had to find a job. Went through a divorce. Became a single mom. Moved to a new city. 
.
I stayed focused on doing my best to raise kind humans and I found a job at home. Last year I lost that job and had to get a serving job. God brought me a man to do life with. 
.
You may be going through a tough season but know God has a plan for you. ♥️
